Comment: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:21.47,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:81476,81476}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100809,102509}How about a little break?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102909,108976}To tell you the truth, I was just getting\Nwarmed up. Let's train a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108976,111476}I agree with Tomiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111976,114876}Okay, assume positions.\NWe'll take that break later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115909,116976}I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119276,124509}I'm so glad that we won our first match.\NGirls got much happier already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124509,128776}If this keeps up,\Nwe'll also win the second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128776,132709}Who knows, maybe we'll\Neven reach the finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133842,137809}Yukari, I thought that out of the two of us,\Nyou were the realistic one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137809,143676}You know best that in sport, motivation boosts\Nthe power by five, or maybe even ten times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143676,147142}There's some truth to it. The most important\Nthing now is not to lose that momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147142,148742}Let's get back to the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148742,149476}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152309,153909}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155142,156609}You're bursting with energy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156609,159342}Yes. We've decided that we'll do\Neverything in our power
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159342,162809}to make it through the qualifiers\Nand advance to the National Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162809,167309}Therefore, sir, please allow me\Nto speak from the manager's point of view
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167309,173309}and ask you to fill the application for\Nthe participation in the National Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173809,176676}I see that you're\Nalready planning ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:03:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177276,180476}Way to go. But for now,\Nlet's focus on your second match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180476,184209}Now listen. The Prefectural Tournament\NCommittee confirmed the schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184209,187576}and you'll play with\NTamagaoka High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187576,189209}Tamagaoka High School?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189976,194209}Yes. Not much is known\Nabout their team, just like ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194942,197176}So we'd better go and learn\Nsomething about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197176,201242}I understand where you're coming from,\Nbut nothing is more important than training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201242,204876}What ultimately matters\Nis the difference in fitness and skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204876,208709}I count on your full commitment in training.\NDo we understand each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208709,209942}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211209,212942}By the way, where's Ichijō?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212942,215142}She didn't come to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215142,217042}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217042,220176}I hope it's only today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220176,226376}It wouldn't be good if she stopped\Nshowing up at school for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236809,238642}– I'm back.\N– Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238642,241676}Asuka, were you at school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241676,242642}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243376,245142}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246176,249142}I'm thinking about\Ndropping out of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249509,252676}Hmm? Is it because your friends\Nfound out about the accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255242,258142}You don't need to feel ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260242,262376}It's true. People are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262376,265442}However, you cannot\Navoid them indefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265442,268276}Sooner or later,\Nyou'll have to face the reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268276,271976}I just don't want\Nto see anyone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271976,274309}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274309,278476}However, remember that without you,\Nyour clubmates will stay on high five.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278842,281942}You probably know\Nwhat that means, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281942,282909}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282909,287176}You just won your first match.\NIf I were them, I'd be very disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302109,305676}{\i1}Ichijō Asuka's absence\Nwas dragging on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305676,309442}{\i1}She didn't show up at school\Nthe next day or the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316576,318342}What's up with Ichijō-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318342,320876}She won't be here today either?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322376,324376}Yes. Let's focus on training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325242,327942}– Sumi'e, tell them.\N– It'll be better if it's you, Tomiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327942,329876}Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329876,334376}What are you mumbling about there?\NIf you want to tell us something, just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334809,336976}All right, just don't hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336976,340142}Once again there are only five of us,\Nso we can't play in the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340142,343076}And if that's the case…\Nwhy are we even training?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347676,349976}There it is,\Nthe beginning of the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351676,355442}I'm sorry, Hijiri-san,\Ncould you make some space for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:06:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357076,362942}{\fscx90\fscy92}Wait a moment. According to the schedule\Napproved by the Student Council, today is our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362942,364609}Oh, we are perfectly aware of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364609,368109}The question is, what's the point\Nin you having the access to the hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368109,371242}when you don't have enough people\Nto participate in official games?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371242,377609}Meanwhile, it's more than likely that our club\Nwill advance to the National Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377609,380042}It's better for us\Nto have access to the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380042,384776}What makes you think that\Nwe can't participate in the games?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384776,386076}Don't give me that nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386076,389976}Stay calm! Yes, I admit it'll make more sense\Nfor your club to practice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391309,392242}Mimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394309,396542}Hijiri-san, surely you're not gonna\Ngive them back the hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396542,399809}If we go by what's better for school,\Nthat's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399809,401709}We can always exercise outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413342,415509}What's that?\NWhy the long faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415509,419576}I'm worried if we'll be able\Nto play the second match.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419576,421009}That's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421009,425609}Unfortunately, I can't do\Nanything about Ichijō's absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425609,428642}Why she doesn't show up\Nat school is her business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428642,432742}I think that you, as her friends,\Ncould do more than me in that regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435442,438576}It can't go on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438576,441309}What do you say if one of us\Nwent to visit her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441309,444942}and she simply asked\Nwhy she doesn't come to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444942,449042}I've thought about it\Nand actually I'd happily do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449042,452476}but I'm afraid that it'd only cause\Nmore harm than good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453609,455242}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455242,458642}Ichijō-san is very independent.\NIf we came to question her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458642,463309}she could understand it so that\Nwe only care about keeping our club alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463309,467876}It could make her want\Nto come to school even less.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467876,470509}Honestly, I feel like going\Nto school less and less myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470509,473109}Don't say that, Yukari!\NYou have to stay with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477676,482309}{\i1}The day after the girls didn't show up\Nat training, thinking up different excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482309,484742}{\i1}Mimi was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495976,497742}What's going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500276,501876}What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511142,512776}Getting old is no picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512776,513776}Grandma, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513776,516642}Isn't she the captain\Nof the Sister's team?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516642,519709}I think she is.\NLet's go to her and say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524142,525509}Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527476,531442}I am Hijiri Mimi's grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531442,536442}Mimi told me you haven't been\Nto school for some time, Ichijō-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536442,539276}I'm glad to see\Nthat you're in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541142,545042}I must tell you, sweetheart, that you and\Nmy granddaughter are like two peas in a pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545042,547942}Like two peas in a pod?\NWhat do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548476,554842}You see, Mimi doesn't even know if you'll be able\Nto play the second match, but she trains anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554842,558676}Ichijō-san, you also can't part\Nwith volleyball, even outside of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558676,560776}You're both obsessed\Nwith this sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562676,564776}Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564776,567042}Good luck in your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594309,596442}Easy, easy!\NNow, to the basket!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603642,604776}Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604776,606442}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607842,609109}I'd like to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609109,615276}What, are you so tired of volleyball\Nthat you came to ask us to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616642,619242}If so, we'll welcome you\Nwith open arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620476,622209}I didn't come for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622209,626342}I wanted to ask you to let me\Ntrain with you a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626342,630009}Train… like, basketball?\NOr volleyball?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630009,632176}A little bit of both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632176,634909}If it's a joke, it's not very funny.\NDon't waste our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634909,636509}But I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636509,640976}I just saw you shoot, Shiraki-san,\Nand I was impressed with your precision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640976,643476}Thank you for the compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643476,645642}But how does this relate\Nto volleyball?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645642,651609}I'd like to be able to send the balls where I want,\Nwith the same kind of accuracy that you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651609,655809}That's why I thought, maybe I could practice\Nreceptions and spikes together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655809,657076}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:11:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657076,660042}You want to practice playing\Nvolleyball into the basket?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660042,661709}Yes. Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661709,663676}There's no way you could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663676,665742}Exactly. Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665742,669142}This is why I want to practice\Nuntil I can, I think that's logical?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669142,670209}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673176,674776}Trouble, big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674776,679009}Hijiri-san went all alone to the basketball club\Nand they're probably gonna fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679009,680642}They're gonna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682509,685209}I'm ready, Shiraki-san!\NPlay with all your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685209,688209}What a nutcase.\NIt will never work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688709,690676}Ready, yes? Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694776,697442}Oh, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697442,699542}Face it, it's impossible.
Comment: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:52.27,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:712276,712276}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714076,716876}It'd be strange if it\Nworked on the first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716876,719076}Shiraki-san, please, let's repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719076,721309}It's pointless,\Nyou're never going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721642,722909}Let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722909,728309}Did you know how to shoot at the basket\Nso precisely since you were born?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729242,730842}Fair point. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732542,734109}Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739142,741476}See? It was closer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741476,743942}With your help,\NI'll master it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743942,749109}Come on. Why should I,\Nthe basketball club captain, help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749609,750576}Because we're—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750576,751742}Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752842,754142}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755142,756209}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756909,760442}No need to apologize.\NYou didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760442,762209}I wanted to talk to you\Nabout something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765009,770776}I wanted to talk to you about the Prefectural\NTournament. The second round is in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770776,774809}However, judging by the current situation,\Nit's unlikely that you'll be able to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774809,777276}So I'm planning to submit a form\Nto withdraw our participation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779342,781776}{\i1}If only Ichijō-san\Nwere here with us…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781976,785809}Hijiri. You don't want to pretend it's all right\Nwhen you don't have enough people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786709,788876}No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788876,792076}I think that at the moment, we have\Nnothing to look for in the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794076,799076}In that case, I won't stall and send the necessary\Npaperwork to the Committee right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801876,804176}Now that we got that out of the way,\Nthere's one last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804176,806709}Are you not interested\Nin what is happening with Ichijō?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813476,814709}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816242,817276}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817276,822542}I'll say this upfront, if you're here to make me\Nplay a second match with you, count me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822542,826342}No, it's too late for that. The coach\Nhas withdrawn us from the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827209,829609}Oh, yeah?\NThen why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830109,835909}There was a lot going on in class when you\Nwere gone. I came with notes and overdue tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835909,837309}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837309,839276}Did you come all the way\Nhere just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839776,843142}Yes. To tell you the truth,\NI wanted to drop by long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843142,849109}But I didn't want you to think that\NI'm here only to pester you about the games.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849109,851576}For better or worse,\Nthe solution presented itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851576,853776}Anyway, I'm glad that\Nwe can avoid misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855476,857242}Hmm? Something smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857676,859242}Oh, it looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861876,864309}I'm sorry.\NI haven't eaten since morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864309,865409}Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865976,868742}Why don't you invite\Nyour friend to eat with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868742,870976}I don't want to impose on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874542,876376}Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877942,880742}My daughter is a great cook.\NShe'll turn anything into a great meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880742,885042}Ichijō-san, I'd like to make it up to you. Maybe\Nyou could come over to eat with us tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885042,886842}At your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886842,890409}I make a terrible cook, but Grandma's food\Nis out of this world. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892742,894376}Say yes, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894376,897542}This is the first time someone\Nhas invited you to their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897542,899409}Come on, it'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899409,901042}With pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901042,902276}Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907509,909409}What? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909409,912109}Please. Let's practice\Nlike the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912109,914476}What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915109,918342}Your club has withdrawn\Nfrom the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918342,922042}Why do you still want to practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922576,926042}Believe me, I want to play\Nmore than you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926042,928042}However, that is not\Nwhy I want to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928742,930276}See, I love volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930276,934342}That's enough for me to want to train.\NI don't need any big goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935009,939376}I just want to do what I like best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939376,941942}What's so strange about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942409,943642}Hijiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944676,945942}I'll play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946909,947942}Sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949209,951176}{\i1}Asuka was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951176,955209}{\i1}Until now, she couldn't trust anyone. She didn't\Nhave anyone who she could call a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955209,959009}{\i1}But today Hijiri Mimi\Ninvited her to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959009,960776}{\i1}Asuka's heart of ice\Nthawed a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960776,964276}{\i1}Maybe… Maybe she'll finally\Nbe able to make friends with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966676,969176}Well, well.\NYou look wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970542,973542}I didn't know there was such a beauty\Nbehind that usual grimace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973542,978976}I'm so proud of you. I'm so glad that\Nyou're finally behaving for your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980742,982976}Here's the cake and\Nthe flowers for a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984109,986076}When are you meeting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986076,988509}At six o'clock, in front of the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989109,993076}I don't know where Hijiri-san lives,\Nso we agreed that she'd show me the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993076,995576}It's quite late.\NYou'd better go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995576,998009}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001376,1002542}{\i1}Darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003942,1006942}{\i1}All signs point that our daughter\Nwill start smiling again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009509,1011276}Let's get started, Hijiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017842,1019309}Mimi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019309,1020542}Mimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036376,1039042}– Hang in there, Mimi!\N– Hijiri-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039276,1040376}Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040376,1042042}Hey! Hijiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065942,1067742}Hijiri, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067742,1069009}What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071509,1073109}Mimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090442,1091642}Ichijō-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091642,1093209}Ichijō-san, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093842,1096209}Why did you come here?!\NGo home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096209,1098009}I'll do anything\Nto make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098009,1101676}But you must know that I did\Nnot forget about our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101676,1102842}Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105276,1108276}The coach trained with me\None on one until late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108276,1109709}You trained?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109709,1113309}But wait, you told me\Nthat you had quit the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114076,1115242}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115242,1117309}But I love volleyball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119376,1121142}What exactly did you practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121142,1124676}I was playing receptions\Nand tried to hit the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124676,1127176}But that's beyond your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127809,1130842}Yes. That's why I wanted\Nto practice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131409,1135376}Unfortunately, I got hit with the ball in the head\Nand I lost consciousness. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139976,1144209}Doesn't matter. Everything's cool now.\NHijiri-san, I'd like to see this exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153376,1155176}I'm ready. Please start!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164542,1166209}One more time, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187242,1189042}All right. Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195576,1197909}You did it! It went in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201776,1203909}Awesome!\NCongratulations, Ichijō-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203909,1205409}I'm so happy.\NI'm so happy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206509,1208909}What exactly are you\Nso happy about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208909,1213609}Because you were able to do something\Nthat others couldn't do. It was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213609,1214909}Like a proper captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216609,1218942}You are the captain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219376,1220209}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221109,1225109}Hijiri-san, you're much more\Nsuited to be the captain than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225109,1230142}Please, become our club's captain\Nand let me come back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235409,1237709}Mimi, I'm joining her request.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237709,1239609}Long live the new captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239609,1241942}Hijiri-san, will you let me\Ncome back to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241942,1244609}It wouldn't be the same\Nwithout you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244609,1247642}Hey, hey, we have six people again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247642,1251142}Looks like we'll be able to play\Nthe second match after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253976,1258542}Yes, but… The coach has already\Nsent the resignation form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260776,1264009}Not quite. For now, I've only filled out\Nthe application, but I haven't sent it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266642,1270142}Now I can say that I wanted\Nto hold off with it until the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270142,1274276}In other words, I never stopped believing in you.\NAnd that is the essence of sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274276,1277276}I told you a little white lie\Nto see how you'd behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277276,1280342}I'm sorry for having\Nmanipulated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281676,1284342}Who would've thought,\Nthe coach knows us better than ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285309,1288176}With such a trainer\Nwe're indestructible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291309,1297076}{\i1}On that day, Tachibana's Volleyball Club\Nfor the first time became truly united.
Comment: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:47.57,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1307576,1307576}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309676,1314076}Sir, please tell us the plan how to play\Nin the tomorrow's match.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.07,0:21:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314076,1316642}In the tomorrow's match?\NThere is no plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316642,1318042}– But sir…\N– Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318042,1321309}Don't tell me you don't know the reason\Nfor the training we started today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321309,1324776}As the second match of the tournament\Napproaches, Mimi and the girls begin to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324776,1330209}They ease up a bit once they find out that Daisuke\Nis already thinking about tactics for the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330209,1332309}In the next episode of\N"Attack on Tomorrow":
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332309,1335442}"Towards the Semi-finals".\NSee you soon!
